title: 怎么删除warp表列权限？
author: Minec-硕
txt_content:
我在控制台打了，可是还是能打开地标表列！
mangdelp Default essentials.warp.list            mangdelp Builder essentials.warp.list

replies.author: Agger_
replies.txt_content: 添加两个权限就可以了 /mangaddp Builder（如果你的默认权限组是这个的话） essentials.warp   和/mangaddp Builder -essentials.warp.list

replies.author: Agger_
replies.txt_content: mangdelp Default essentials.warp  输入这个指令试试 不行在回复

replies.author: Minec-硕
replies.txt_content:
Agger_ 发表于 2015-2-9 12:33
mangdelp Default essentials.warp  输入这个指令试试 不行在回复
还是不行，仍然打得开
